1) Get http://developers.facebook.com/clientlibs/facebook-platform.tar.gz
2) Extract

If you have php4.
3) As per facebook instructions..
   3a) Get http://downloads.sourceforge.net/ister4framework/simplexml44-0_4_4.tar.gz
   3b) Extract to facebook-platform/php4client

4) Signup for a developer account:
*  http://www.facebook.com/developers/apps.php
   * Site Callback should be http://www.domain.com/facebook/ (with domain.com being your newly setup site)
   * Keys can be filled in at /admin/settings/facebook_auth


NOTE:
If you do nothave clean urls turned on, make sure to set your return url to http://www.domain.com/ instead of http://www.domain.com/facebook/
